			'''
			Grants immunity to [i:ThoriumRework/QueenJellyPin]Bubbled, [i:ThoriumRework/VampireCape]Bleeding, [i:ThoriumRework/VampireCape]Vampire's Curse and [i:ThoriumRework/DeepDarkShellShield]knockback
