			[i:ThoriumRework/BeholderTentacles][i:ThoriumRework/StriderMouthguard] Attacks inflict Frostbite and Hellfire, deal increased damage to, and gain shield from targets affected by either debuffs
			[i:ThoriumRework/StriderMouthguard][i:ThoriumRework/UndyingGaze] Hold attack to generate up to three Frost Mytes, stop attacking to unleash them, granting Soul Essence on hit
			[i:ThoriumRework/DeepDarkShellShield][i:ThoriumRework/BandofCratons] Grants a passive 40 shield, immunity to Overflowed and makes your attacks inflict it, and doubles the health boost from shield while also increasing defensive stats
			[i:ThoriumRework/BandofCratons] Restores player resources based on the amount of shield lost, losing more than 20 shield creates an electric shock that destroys 3 projectiles
			[i:ThoriumRework/UndyingGaze] Critical strikes grant Soul Essence, attacks that use life or already grant Soul Essence give more
			[i:ThoriumRework/QueenJellyPin] Summons tentacles around you that latches onto enemies which boost life and resource regeneration on hit, tentacle damage increases based on defense
			[i:ThoriumRework/VampireCape] You take significantly less damage and much less likely to be targeted by enemies while Bat Swarm is active
			[i:ThoriumRework/ZephyrWings] Grappling in the air with Zephyr's Grip's hatchling extends flight time
			[i:ThoriumRework/ZephyrWings] Zephyr's Grip's hatchling can be summoned again after gliding for a bit, dealing damage replenishes it faster
			[i:ThoriumRework/StarScoutReticle] Allows breathing in space and grants night vision
			[i:ThoriumRework/StarScoutReticle] Dashing teleports you a few blocks forward and gives you a dash if you don't have one yet
			[i:ThoriumRework/BannerofWar] Damage and bonus healing increases over time while in combat but gradually fade when out of combat
			[i:ThoriumRework/BannerofWar] While in combat, periodically emit a pulse that heals allies equal to bonus healing, bard empowerment range affects the range, and the frequency increases over time
